summary: An email from May 3, 2021, regarding a call about photo metadata related to Ghislaine Maxwell, sent between FBI personnel and US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS) contractors. The email is marked as external and includes an attachment.

events.title: Call about Maxwell photo metadata
events.description: A call was held regarding photo metadata related to Ghislaine Maxwell.

keyFacts: The document is an email dated May 3, 2021, concerning a call about photo metadata related to Ghislaine Maxwell.
The email was sent between FBI personnel and US Attorney's Office for the Southern District of New York (USANYS) contractors.
The email is marked as external and includes an attachment, though the attachment's content is not described in the provided text.
